title: Sally in wonderland
description:
little Sally Acorn as Alice in "Alice in wonderland"
i very love this story. especially the Disney version, and even now we are adult now. we still can not forget those cute memory which always play with us when we are little.
that means the important of keeping our child innocent ,this is the wisdom of child,

when i saw Sally at first, i think she is a very very charming and elegant pretty girl. so i always drew her as the very megical and mature lady just like the elves

but than i saw many good artworker can drew Sally as the very very cute little innocent girl. so...i want to gave a try. try to drew Sally to be the cute little character

OK!so!this is my experiment's result, and i think is good....

NO!not good!it is...it is...AWSOME!!!><i can't can't believe she can be sooooooooo adorable!!!it must be the little angel from God!

reall!i not kidding!this is the first time ever! i think my artwork is excellent!!!i like it!i can't live without her!i can't sleep without this cute little girl!
i rrrrrreally love it!so i hope you love it too!!!!^^

OK!Sally is as Alice in the story "Alice in wonderland" ..look at her cute little face and lovely little pink dress.

-------------------------------------

Sally open a few doors...she enter a very weird room....she can saw a little door on the corner...she running in front of it and pull the door knob
"OH!"the door knob suddenly shouted!little Sally shocked!and quickly pull over her hand!

"oh!MY!oh....sorry...!"she put her hand on her face and apology

"that's all right!...but you have a really big strange!little dear!"the door knob smiling and said

"please....sir..."Sally said it in the innocent voice.

"Hohoho!don't worry!little girl!by the way!what is your name?"

"Sally...Sally...Acorn..."

"lovely name!sweet heart!what can i do for you?"

"well...i'm...looking for a rabbit...can you help me...?"

"oh!you mean her?"the door knob open his mouth- the keyhole, and little girl look at the hole, she can see something..."A!it's Bunnie!there she is! i must ...."

"OH!no!no!you can not pass!"the door knob said"you are too big...little cute..."

Sally put her head down"so..it is impossable....."

"nono!there is nothing impossable!it's just you can't!why don't you try the thing on the table!"

"Table?"Sally look back. she found out a glass table appear!and a glass bottle on the table.she quickly run to the table and pick the bottle up, she can see a little note on the bottle "drink me"

little Sally is curious.
"mm.....i don't know what will happen....but...i 'm...just give my self a advice....all right...."and she drink a little...

"not bad...taste like....cherry jam..."but she do not realize, she is getting smaller a little bit
"or...apple pie...?"she smaller more!and smaller and smaller...
"lemon juice,rooster!or...oh!my!goodness!"she can't hold the "giant"glass bottle and fall down

she standing up and grab her little skirt so tightly
"my goodness!what happen to me?"
"Hoo!Ho!you look just like a little candle !sweet girl!"


--TO BE CONTINUED--
